Why This Exists
In 2011, Iran captured a US military drone using GPS Spoofing.
Drones today still have NO way to verify if a GPS signal is real.
DroneChain fixes this using blockchain as a trusted source of truth.

 What DroneChain Does
- Every GPS signal is verified against blockchain before drone accepts it
- Trusted satellite sources stored immutably on-chain
- Every spoofing attempt logged permanently — cannot be deleted
- Drone stays safe even during signal jamming attacks

